Smriti Shyamal is currently doing Ph.D. at [https://mcmaster.ca McMaster University], Canada, where
he is supervised   
by [http://macc.mcmaster.ca/profile.php?personid=120 Dr. Christoper L.E. Swartz]. He received 
B.Tech degree from [http://www.iitb.ac.in Indian Institute of Technology, Bombay],
India in 2013 and subsequently joined [https://mcmaster.ca McMaster University]. His current
research focus is on data science, machine learning, optimization and control applications.

